data.description: Honey, stop the car! Stunning single-family home on a Cul De Sac, located in the desirable Spencer's Crossing Community! This two-story residence offers a perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality, with PAID IN FULL SOLAR!! Entering the home, you are greeted by luxury vinyl planking. The Family room is huge! Large upgraded double slider windows allow natural light to fill the room. The gorgeous fireplace creates a warm and inviting atmosphere. The Family room is open to the Beautiful kitchen and dinning area. The well-appointed kitchen is a chef's dream, complete plenty of cabinet space and a huge center island that provides ample room for meal preparation. The kitchen features white cabinets with brushed gold hardware, a designer backsplash, and designer lighting, adding a touch of elegance to the space. The built-in stove with an upgraded range is a standout feature that will delight any cooking enthusiast. The open concept design of the kitchen and dining area allows for seamless entertaining and easy interaction with guests. There is a main level bedroom, providing flexibility and convenience. This room can be used as a guest bedroom, a home office, or a playroom. The remaining four bedrooms are located upstairs. There is also a half bathroom downstairs. The primary suite is a luxurious retreat, featuring a generous-sized bedroom, a walk-in closet, and an en-suite bathroom with separate dual sinks, a soaking tub, and a separate shower. Additionally, there are three more spacious bedrooms and a full bathroom on this level, providing ample space for family members or guests. One of the standout features of this home is the large loft/bonus room. This versatile space can be transformed into a home office, a media room, a playroom, or a gym. The backyard is just the right size! Beautiful lawn and a patio area. The built-in lighted stucco patio adds to the overall charm of the home. Spencer's Crossing offers easy access to a variety of amenities. Nearby, you'll find schools, shopping centers & restaurants. The community itself boasts a range of amenities, including pools, parks, walking trails, and clubhouse. Very Close to the Brand New Liberty High School! This home has it all!
